statement.p:
The slopes of several lines are given below. Which of the lines are parallel to the graph of y=0.75x+2, and which are perpendicular to it?

\dfrac{3}{4}

\dfrac{8}{6}

\dfrac{-20}{15}

\dfrac{-39}{52}

\dfrac{4}{3}

\dfrac{-16}{12}

\dfrac{36}{48}

\dfrac{9}{12}

